            dl.timeline-series
              dt#Policy08.timeline-event
                a Letter from Secretary, Department of Telecommunications on rise in frequency of internet shutdowns. D.O. No.: 800-37/2016-AS.II/1

              dd.timeline-event-content#Policy08EX
