                  | On the basis of RTI responses, we found that there were at least 26 unreported instances of Internet shutdowns in Rajasthan alone during the eight-odd months in question. A detailed blogpost about the responses from Rajasthan to our RTI applications can be viewed here, https://sflc.in/rti-reply-rajasthan-home-department-reveals-21-unreported-internet-shutdowns.

